{"tid":2018771,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"提升空場比賽氛圍，巴塞將在LED屏幕上播放球迷照片","createTime":"2020-05-15T22:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T03:16:04.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c158b16ce000ca5279e4220236c9e5b8fa6e3fb","tid":2018771,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:20:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/club/news/1668986/lets-win-this-match-together-an-initiative-to-show-support-for-the-players-when-football-returns-to-camp-nou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcbarcelona.com%2Fen%2Fclub%2Fnews%2F1668986%2Flets-win-this-match-together-an-initiative-to-show-support-for-the-players-when-football-returns-to-camp-nou&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=c16a618f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/club/news/1668986/lets-win-this-match-together-an-initiative-to-show-support-for-the-players-when-football-returns-to-camp-nou</a><br />\n<br />\n西甲複賽後也將要空場比賽，巴薩聯合合作商CUPRA準備提升空場比賽的氛圍，將在諾坎普LED屏幕上播放球迷照片。<br />\n<br />\n 在名為&ldquo;讓我們一起贏得這場比賽&rdquo;的活動中，來自世界各地的球迷可以將自己的照片品牌官網，表達對球隊的支持。 當空場比賽時， 會在諾坎普的LED屏幕上顯示球迷們發來的照片。 這樣一來，即使球場內沒有球迷，比賽球員們也可以感受到、看到球迷對巴薩球員的支持。<br />\n<br />\n 巴薩門將特爾施特根也表示：&ldquo;在諾坎普球場的比賽總是很特別的，球迷們的支持也是非常重要的。這項計劃非常棒，可以讓我們感受球迷們的存在，我們需要 適應這種情況，這樣我們就可以為我們主場的比賽創造一種勝利的氣氛。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"01d4b36bbb1acef93e7eeeb564196824a092e856","tid":2018771,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:28.000Z","msg":"不如奪冠隊播fifa慶祝畫面啦 球員都唔洗落場"},{"pid":"2222b5792fbedcdfa902d518d20525b0ce91f5f8","tid":2018771,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"01d4b36bbb1acef93e7eeeb564196824a092e856","tid":2018771,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:28.000Z","msg":"不如奪冠隊播fifa慶祝畫面啦 球員都唔洗落場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"諗起 美斯拎完世界盃，記得關ps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 